VALUES 
(1, 'Goa, India', 5, 2, 35000, ARRAY['Beach', 'Water Sports', 'Nightlife'], '2025-12-20', '2025-12-24', 'Day 1 (Dec 20): Arrival in Goa - Flight arrives at Dabolim Airport at 3 PM - Check-in at beachfront resort in Baga - Evening stroll on Baga Beach - Dinner at shack restaurant Day 2 (Dec 21): Water Sports & North Goa - Morning parasailing at Baga Beach - Lunch at restaurant - Visit Aguada Fort - Evening DJ party Day 3 (Dec 22): South Goa Exploration - Day trip to South Goa via scooter rental - Visit Palolem Beach - Sunset cruise in backwaters - Seafood dinner in Palolem Day 4 (Dec 23): Relaxation & Spa - Morning yoga session - Full body Ayurvedic massage - Shopping at Anjuna Flea Market - Local market exploration Day 5 (Dec 24): Departure - Checkout at 11 AM - Last-minute shopping at duty-free - Flight departure at 8 PM'),
(1, 'Jaipur, Rajasthan, India', 4, 3, 45000, ARRAY['Heritage', 'Culture', 'Shopping'], '2026-01-10', '2026-01-13', 'Day 1 (Jan 10): City Palace & Jantar Mantar - Arrival at Jaipur Railway Station - Hotel check-in in Pink City area - Visit City Palace - Explore Jantar Mantar Observatory - Evening walk in Hawa Mahal bazaar area - Dinner at local restaurant Day 2 (Jan 11): Hawa Mahal & Heritage Walk - Sunrise at Hawa Mahal - Heritage walking tour - Visit Albert Hall Museum - Shopping at Bapu Bazaar - Traditional Rajasthani lunch - Block printing workshop Day 3 (Jan 12): Amber Fort Excursion - Day trip to Amber Fort (30 km away) - Jeep ride up to fort - Complete fort tour with guide - Lunch at restaurant - Visit Jal Mahal on the way back - Shopping at local markets Day 4 (Jan 13): Departure - Last-minute souvenir shopping - Checkout and departure to airport - Flight/train departure in evening'),
(1, 'Kochi & Alleppey, Kerala, India', 6, 2, 80000, ARRAY['Nature', 'Backwaters', 'Relaxation', 'Food'], '2025-11-15', '2025-11-20', 'Day 1 (Nov 15): Arrival in Kochi - Flight arrival at Kochi International Airport - Check-in at houseboat resort - Sunset cruise on backwaters - Traditional Kerala dinner Day 2 (Nov 16): Kochi Exploration - Visit Chinese Fishing Nets - Tour of Paradesi Synagogue - Spice market exploration - Sunset at Fort Kochi beach - Dinner at Kashi Art Cafe Day 3 (Nov 17): Houseboat Backwaters - All-day houseboat cruise - Stop at coconut lagoons - Traditional fishing net demonstration - On-board lunch with fish curry - Sunset view from houseboat Day 4 (Nov 18): Alleppey Beach & Water Sports - Transfer to Alleppey - Water sports: kayaking & paddleboarding - Beach volleyball session - Traditional Kerala lunch at beach shack - Sunset beach walk Day 5 (Nov 19): Spa & Relaxation - Ayurvedic treatment session - Visit Kumbalangi Sanctuary - Birdwatching tour - Local elephant sanctuary - Evening meditation session Day 6 (Nov 20): Departure - Breakfast at resort - Last-minute shopping for spices and handicrafts - Transfer to airport - Flight departure');
